      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HARA'S PEST (3) is racing well without winning, recording five minors on end, the latest hitting the ground running with a fast early sectional but finishing in the minors again when third (21.93) over 380m at this track. Has won three of five starts from this draw. Top chance in this line up. GIDGEE BUG (2) has been in the money at his last two runs, most recently when second beaten 3.5 lengths (28.76). Drops back in trip for this. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Well placed and gets his chance. MOONSHINE MAGIC (1) could manage only seventh after making contact in the run last time in a Free For All at this track, finishing 3.5 lengths from the winner (22.31). Better than last start and can bounce back. VILLAIN OF FIRE (8) form at this distance reads well.",
